\s TURIMO KURWANA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Turimo kurwana n’umwami w’iyi si adukururira mu nyigisho mbi yihangiye ariko Umugeni wa Yesu ari maso kuko yamenye ko iyi si igiye kurimbuka.\bd*\bd x2\bd*\bd  \bd*
\pc \bdit [Mana] turi mu rugendo [kuko] waduhampagaye udukura mu rufatanye rw’amadini [udu]kuremo kamere [yake]ra twahoranyeyo tugende twuzuye imbaraga zo mu gihe cya nyuma.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umuhanuzi Eliya twamaze kumubona niwe waduhishuriye inzira dukwiye kunyuramo kuko Baburoni yari yarayisibye kugira ngo Ijambo ry’Ukuri Ritatugeraho.\bd*\bd x2\bd*\bd  \bd*
\pc \bdit [Mana] turi mu rugendo [kuko] waduhampagaye udukura mu rufatanye rw’amadini [udu]kuremo kamere [yake]ra twahoranyeyo tugende twuzuye imbaraga zo mu gihe cya nyuma.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Turi ku rufatiro rw’Intumwa n’Abahanuzi twizera umubatizo mw’Izina rya Yesu kuko ariryo twahawe ngo dukirizwemo inzego eshatu nizo Yesu yigaragajemo.\bd*\bd x2\bd*
